440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 187}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "去旅游你会不会发朋友圈？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-3be8625d42e51757170ed52f7af6a39f_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "68 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1933109560891142584"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIwcPb+puX1dAQEAMaCTExNTk3NjU0MSDyvJvEBjAAOLEBQBRyEzE5MzMxMDk1NjA4OTExNDI1ODR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "21_1777689829.388215", "card_id": "Q_30651530", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 170}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "加拿大的石油储备世界第二，为什么大家似乎都关注中东的石油为多呢？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "加拿大是美国进口石油的最大来源国，可是媒体上经常提到美国是为了中东的石油而战，让人感觉中东才是最大的石油来源。如何解释这一貌似矛盾的现象？（出处：《第三次工业革命》2012 年 6 月第 1 版 P189)"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/881f9d64e8950f2c7bc308b4e7d9a029_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "64 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/30651530"}}, "attached_info": "Cj0IwcPb+puX1dAQEAMaBzQ0NDI5Mzgg15aKqwUwADiEDEAVcggzMDY1MTUzMHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "22_1777689829.388581", "card_id": "Q_2033136302892085784", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 59}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "香飘飘 2025 年净利润大降 62.38%，你还在喝香飘飘冲泡奶茶吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "2025 年香飘飘实现营业收入 29.26 亿元，同比 2024 年的 32.87 亿元下滑 11.00%，已连续两年同比下降。分产品来看，冲泡类业务是营收下滑的主要拖累项，全年实现收入 18.81 亿元，同比大降 17.20%；即饮类业务则保持稳健增长，实现收入 10.05 亿元，同比增长 3.27%。 分区域来看，华中地区营收下滑最为显著，全年收入 3.73 亿元，同比大降 25.43%；华东作为公司最大收入区域，全年收入 12.38 亿元，同比下滑 15.54%。不过出口和直营渠道实现逆势增长，出口收入 0.34 亿元，同比大增 77.55%；直营收入 1.33 亿元，同比增长 71.56%。香飘飘 2025 年报解读：归母净利润大降 62.38%，研发费用大增 47.50%"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-ba8bf9dc303b127b6bdbdbf00b251f32_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2033136302892085784"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIwcPb+puX1dAQEAMaCTExOTMzNTE2OCCch8vPBjAAOIgBQBZyEzIwMzMxMzYzMDI4OTIwODU3ODR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "23_1777689829.389119", "card_id": "Q_39501051", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 35}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "数学学到什么程度可以进行下一部分的学习了？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "在学习一部分内容的时候总会觉得没有学透或者没有学完，那如何判断 自己什么时候可以进行下一部分知识的学习？ 题主是数系本科生，看书主要是想扩充知识面，加强对数学各个方向一些粗浅的了解。 但最近在一本书中停留太久，不知道该接下来继续看完？还是先换个方向换本书？ 这种想法是否正确？这个问题应该如何解决？ 谢谢。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-70a0c6e5cf9c89df1f15aa22dce86cf9.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/39501051"}}, "attached_info": "Cj0IwcPb+puX1dAQEAMaBzgwMDc1MzggmZ3htAUwADj3FUAXcggzOTUwMTA1MXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "24_1777689829.389514", "card_id": "Q_2033497493866898865", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 133}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "2 名储户 1800 万存款离奇失踪，银行员工已被被采取强制措施，钱还能追回来吗？银行该负责还钱吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "近日，原扶余惠民村镇银行（现已更名为吉林农商银行扶余支行）发生的千万存款莫名流失事件经媒体报道后，引发社会广泛关注。 4 月 30 日，吉林农商银行有关负责人表示，该行对原扶余惠民村镇银行相关存款事件高度重视，正全力配合司法机关开展调查，依法依规推进处置。原扶余惠民村镇银行涉案员工赵某丽已被公安机关依法采取强制措施。被盗取的储户存款由公安机关依法追查追缴；针对客户合理诉求，该行将严格遵循「存款自愿、取款自由」原则，不等待司法结论，依法合规保障客户合法权益。 此次事件充分暴露出原扶余惠民村镇银行在内控合规、风险管控等方面存在明显漏洞和短板。吉林农商银行在吸收合并原扶余惠民村镇银行后，已第一时间就相关问题报案，并对相关责任人进行问责处理。该行将深刻汲取教训，举一反三，全面排查内控薄弱环节，完善制度流程，强化合规管控，坚决杜绝同类问题再次发生。 扶余市公安局相关负责人介绍，目前犯罪嫌疑人已被依法采取刑事强制措施、批准逮捕并移送审查起诉，案件尚未正式进入公诉阶段，具体案情暂不便对外披露。 据大象新闻此前报道，吉林省的陈冰（化名）反映，半年前，她将 1000 万元现金存入吉林省扶余市的扶余惠民村镇银行，如今存款却离奇失踪。她的存款丢失不久后，涉事银行的储户王女士遇到了相似的情况，存在该行的 800 万存款去向不明。如今几个月过去了，两人这 1800 万存款何时能取出？至今银行方面也没有一个回复。 银行千万存款离奇失踪：员工赵某丽已被采取强制措施"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/100/v2-a4472653558e6573dfd9888a2e5765d8_r.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "58 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2033497493866898865"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIwcPb+puX1dAQEAMaCTExOTM0NzE1NiD/p9DPBjAAOIcDQBhyEzIwMzM0OTc0OTM4NjY4OTg4NjV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "25_1777689829.390269", "card_id": "Q_1950196908518774319", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 20}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "信息论的本质是什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-b1d2f7c5a84320dd4aaa535521469540_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "58 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1950196908518774319"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIwcPb+puX1dAQEAMaCTExNjU3MjU5MyDHkJTGBjAAOIUBQBlyEzE5NTAxOTY5MDg1MTg3NzQzMTl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "26_1777689829.390514", "card_id": "Q_1897263710768169725", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 50}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "送外卖都什么感受啊，好送吗?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "想试试送外卖"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-2ca8eaeefe43d89a019e9e8119cdca51_1440w.webp"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "58 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1897263710768169725"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIwcPb+puX1dAQEAMaCTExNDU5MTM3OSDm7JHABjAAOEpAGnITMTg5NzI2MzcxMDc2ODE2OTcyNXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1777689829.390850", "card_id": "Q_2030665204166563335", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 46}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待富野由悠季称「现在高达迷喜欢说高达战斗好帅」「后辈做高达动画无战争气息」“没教会他们是我的错？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "关联 如何看待富野由悠季称「动漫内容充斥在生活场景里」让他「忍不住觉得」「这些东西简直是在玷污日本文化」？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-d4706bea7d615304a2005e5645c0988f_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "57 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2030665204166563335"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIwcPb+puX1dAQEAMaCTExOTI1MTk5OSC4jKfPBjAAOEdAG3ITMjAzMDY2NTIwNDE2NjU2MzMzNXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1777689829.391254", "card_id": "Q_2020055937386328647", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 234}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "小米手机毛利率跌至 8.3%，卢伟冰称涨价需理解，这会如何影响其性价比策略？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "本文来源：时代财经 作者：庞宇 张照 图源：视觉中国 3 月 24 日晚，小米集团（01810.HK）发布了 2025 年业绩报告，全年收入首次突破 4000 亿元大关，达到 4572.87 亿元，同比增长 25%；公司拥有人应占利润 416.43 亿元，同比增长 76.02%；经调整净利润 391.66 亿元，同比增长 43.8%。全年收入和净利润均创下历史新高。 小米管理层直言 2025 年是小米「实现历史性跨越的一年」，并放话称，2026 年开始，预估未来五年累计研发开支将超过 2000 亿元。 但亮眼财报下，眼下的小米仍面对诸多经营层面的挑战。 去年第四季度，小米实现收入 1169.17 亿元，同比增长 7.3%，这是其连续 5 个季度突破千亿；但经调整净利润同比下滑 23.7% 至 63.40 亿元。作为小米「支柱」的智能手机业务，正面临收入下滑和 内存成本上涨 带来的双重压力。 在当晚电话会上，小米集团合伙人、集团总裁 卢伟冰 坦言：「内存成本的上涨幅度比我们原来预测的还要更加激进。」相较于友商已迫于成本压力上调终端价格的情况，其称小米所面临的压力亦非常大，「我们只是比别人多扛了一会，但是涨价的趋势不可避免」。 智能手机业务承压，友商已在涨价 分业务板块看，小米的手机、 IoT 、互联网服务等业务仍是核心收入来源。手机×AIoT 分部 2025 年全年实现收入 3512.17 亿元，同比增长 5.4%。该分部整体毛利率为 21.7%，同比增长 0.5 个百分点。 不过更细分来看，收入占比最高的智能手机业务的日子「并不好过」。 2025 年，小米智能手机业务全年收入为 1864.40 亿元，同比下滑 2.77%。同时，受国家补贴退坡及核心零部件价格上涨等因素影响，智能手机业务毛利率从 2024 年的 12.6% 下滑至 2025 年的 10.9%。其中，第四季度毛利率为 8.3%，相较上年同期的 12%，下降 3.7 个百分点。 数据显示，过去一年，小米智能手机「量价齐跌」 「扛不住」内存涨价潮：小米手机毛利率跌至 8.3%，卢伟冰喊话若涨价「多些理解」"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4b4a80ff6dd3f9f1b5d1938411ac5fd2.jpg?source=1a5df958"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "56 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2020055937386328647"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIwcPb+puX1dAQEAMaCTExODg4ODkwNiCS24zOBjAAOMYDQBxyEzIwMjAwNTU5MzczODYzMjg2NDd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1777689829.392274", "card_id": "Q_27418122", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 455}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "怎么样才是真正的休息?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "放假在家躺在床上也不觉得很满足 起床之后还是很累 所以怎么样才能让自己得到充分的放松和能量呢"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-c0a7ad220e0cc05268d71af911f58635_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "56 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/27418122"}}, "attached_info": "Cj0IwcPb+puX1dAQEAMaBzMxNTAxMzMg3K+qpQUwADivKUAdcggyNzQxODEyMngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "is_start": false, "next": "", "previous": "", "totals": 0}, "fresh_text": "热榜已更新", "display_num": 15, "display_first": true, "fb_bill_main_rise": 0, "head_zone": {"type": "billboard_lantern", "data": [{"id": "1989780245977532317", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/appview/community_construction", "title": "辟谣专区", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMTk4OTc4MDI0NTk3NzUzMjMxN3ITMTk4OTc4MDI0NTk3NzUzMjMxN3gA", "tag": "辟谣", "tag_bg_color": "GRD01A"}]}, "head_zones": [{"type": "billboard_lantern", "data": [{"id": "1989780245977532317", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/appview/community_construction", "title": "辟谣专区", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMTk4OTc4MDI0NTk